    "image_scrolling_NKhtJw": {
      "type": "image-scrolling",
      "blocks": {
        "row_iFPfQT": {
          "type": "row",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/About-us-banner.webp",
            "cwd": 500,
            "txtbg": "#f5f5f5",
            "bgg": "",
            "talign": "tl",
            "titles": "NOCTURA®",
            "scl": "#000000",
            "sfs": 12,
            "sfw": "500",
            "title": "The Night Has a Dress Code.",
            "htag": "h2",
            "tff": "ft3",
            "fs": 24,
            "fsm": 18,
            "fw": "500",
            "lh": 1.3,
            "cl": "#000000",
            "tmb": 15,
            "tmbm": 10,
            "text": "<p>Not everyone gets it. Not everyone should.</p><p><strong>NOCTURA is a Gen Z streetwear brand born out of Mumbai </strong>- its nights, its music, its energy, and the kind of people who live loudly without asking for permission. Every piece we drop is built for the moment you walk in and the room shifts. Bold graphics. Premium cuts.</p><p>Oversized silhouettes. A fearless aesthetic that hits harder after dark. This isn't the fashion you follow. This is the fashion you feel.</p><p>From Electric Love shirts that come alive under flash, to There Are No Saints sleeveless cuts that own a room - every NOCTURA drop tells a story. Inspired by nightlife, rebellion, street culture, and the raw energy of youth, our collections are designed for the ones chasing nights out, club fits, city streets, and every moment in between.</p>",
            "tfs": 15,
            "tfsm": 13,
            "tlh": 1.6,
            "tcl": "#333333",
            "txtmb": 25,
            "txtmbm": 20,
            "btn": "",
            "link": "",
            "btn-style": "btn1",
            "btn-size": "btn-md"
          }
        },
        "row_HMBCRH": {
          "type": "row",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "cwd": 500,
            "txtbg": "#f5f5f5",
            "bgg": "",
            "talign": "tl",
            "titles": "ADD A TAGLINE",
            "scl": "#000000",
            "sfs": 12,
            "sfw": "500",
            "title": "Spring Summer New Arrival",
            "htag": "h2",
            "tff": "ft1",
            "fs": 24,
            "fsm": 20,
            "fw": "500",
            "lh": 1.3,
            "cl": "#000000",
            "tmb": 15,
            "tmbm": 10,
            "text": "<p>Pair large text with an image to give focus to your chosen product, collection, or blog post. Add details on availability, style, or even provide a review.</p>",
            "tfs": 14,
            "tfsm": 13,
            "tlh": 1.6,
            "tcl": "#666666",
            "txtmb": 25,
            "txtmbm": 20,
            "btn": "SHOP NOW",
            "link": "/",
            "btn-style": "btn1",
            "btn-size": "btn-md"
          }
        },
        "row_JYjHYE": {
          "type": "row",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/about-us2-community.webp",
            "cwd": 500,
            "txtbg": "#fff9fb",
            "bgg": "",
            "talign": "tl",
            "titles": "",
            "scl": "#000000",
            "sfs": 12,
            "sfw": "500",
            "title": "More Than a Brand. A Community.",
            "htag": "h2",
            "tff": "ft3",
            "fs": 24,
            "fsm": 18,
            "fw": "500",
            "lh": 1.3,
            "cl": "#000000",
            "tmb": 15,
            "tmbm": 10,
            "text": "<p>NOCTURA isn't just something you wear - it's something you belong to. We host events, build communities, shoot nights that look like films, and create spaces where fashion lovers actually connect. <strong>If you're part of NOCTURA, you already know. If you're not yet - you will be.</strong><br/><br/>We are not driven by trends. We are driven by culture.</p>",
            "tfs": 15,
            "tfsm": 13,
            "tlh": 1.6,
            "tcl": "#333333",
            "txtmb": 25,
            "txtmbm": 20,
            "btn": "",
            "link": "",
            "btn-style": "btn1",
            "btn-size": "btn-md"
          }
        },
        "row_cGH7am": {
          "type": "row",
          "settings": {
            "cwd": 500,
            "txtbg": "#f2f9f9",
            "bgg": "",
            "talign": "tl",
            "titles": "",
            "scl": "#000000",
            "sfs": 12,
            "sfw": "500",
            "title": "The Founders",
            "htag": "h2",
            "tff": "ft3",
            "fs": 24,
            "fsm": 18,
            "fw": "500",
            "lh": 1.3,
            "cl": "#000000",
            "tmb": 15,
            "tmbm": 10,
            "text": "<p><strong>Paarth:</strong> I didn't start NOCTURA because I wanted to sell clothes. I started it because every time we went out, I couldn't find anything worth wearing. Mumbai has insane energy - the nights, the music, the people and none of that was showing up in what we were putting on. </p><p>So we built it ourselves. NOCTURA is for the ones who feel that same gap. We're not filling a market. We're filling for a moment.<br/><br/><strong>Siddhant:</strong> For me it was always about the aesthetic. The way a piece looks under flash. The way a graphic hits when the lighting's right. I wanted to make clothes that felt like they belonged to a night you'd actually remember. </p><p>Every design I've put into NOCTURA comes from real nights, real energy, nothing corporate. This brand is personal. And that's exactly why it works.</p>",
            "tfs": 15,
            "tfsm": 13,
            "tlh": 1.6,
            "tcl": "#333333",
            "txtmb": 25,
            "txtmbm": 20,
            "btn": "",
            "link": "",
            "btn-style": "btn1",
            "btn-size": "btn-md"
          }
        }
      },
